"title": "8630: worship, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8630",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Worship not only gives God what is due to him but also results in many benefits for his people.</p>\n<h2>True worship brings benefits for God's people</h2>\n<h3>Blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:25-Exod23:26\">EXO 23:25–23:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:13-Deut11:15\">DEU 11:13–11:15</a></p>\n<h3>Guidance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:2–13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6-Isa58:11\">ISA 58:6–58:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:89\">NUM 7:89</a></p>\n<h3>Deliverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25-Acts16:26\">ACT 16:25–16:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:14-Ps50:15\">PSA 50:14–50:15</a></p>\n<h3>Joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:21-1Chr29:22\">1CH 29:21–29:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:30\">2CH 29:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:4\">PSA 43:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:7\">ISA 56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:52\">LUK 24:52</a></p>\n<h3>A sense of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13-2Chr5:14\">2CH 5:13–5:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1KI 8:10–8:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:35\">EXO 40:35</a></p>\n<h3>A deeper sense of Jesus Christ's lordship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:9–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:10-Rev1:18\">REV 1:10–1:18</a></p>\n<h2>Boldness to witness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:9\">PSA 57:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:10\">ACT 18:9–18:10</a></p>\n<h2>True worship convicts sinners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a></strong></p>",
